        "subject": "LU-2576 osc: Add timeout for debugging purposes",
        "message": "LU-2576 osc: Add timeout for debugging purposes\n\nThis change adds a 10 minute timeout to the wait event. If the process\nis not woken up in 10 minutes a message is printed to the console and it\ngoes back to waiting indefinitely.\n\nThis is solely for debugging and not intended to be landed.\n\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I0a75447ca0d7dbe483aa3dd58fb3d1423982bc34\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
